    "text": [
        "Children upbringing has a significant role for parents, but it would be more prominent to raise a child with a family. Many think that bringing up a child is only parent responsibility. Thus, I will make points in further paragraphs to form an opinion.",
        "",
        "On one hand, raising children with the aid of the family, it\u2019s effective rather than take care only by parents. Uncles, aunts, and household members have the expertise to tackle the situation created by a child. In addition, they have past experience and different practical observations on child movements. They know the approach of a child\u2019s body indication. For instance, if the baby is not sleeping, their aunt stories and lullaby helps them to bring sleep. Most of the infants are fond of grandparents because grandparents know how to take care of a baby & how to make them gleeful. Also, these situations are even more remunerative for parents because they want time to bring back their past days and make a relationship stronger than earlier. Raising them is not an easy job and take the decision is even more arduous to do. Thus, family member opinions are helpful to smooth the conditions.",
        "On the other hand, more perspectives make the situation difficult. Some parents believe that parenting should be done by them because they do not want inessential views to raise an infant. Nowadays, parents feel insecure to give a baby to anyone because child trafficking cases are increasing gradually. They consult a pediatrician for a decision they have to take to raise a baby.",
        "",
        "To summarize, in this hectic world, sometimes parents are tired because of the children. In that situation, they feel that family members are equally important. Continuously care of them can create a disrelish approach towards them. Household members have warmth. Hence, Family is beneficial, it adding happiness to an infant as well as for them and this will form a joyful environment for a child."
